The paper also touches on topics related to multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with image synthesis and image quality. 

The use of deep learning and neural networks also suggests that the paper could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category. 

The paper's focus on perceptual similarity and human perception suggests that it could also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. 

Finally, the paper's use of deep learning and neural networks for image synthesis and quality assessment could also place it in the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
